revisions.description: V01.00.00 Initial version of the DCM MIB.
V01.00.01 Added dcmConfigInputTsTable, such that (board, port, UDP, IP) can be converted into an input TS index with a single SNMP GETNEXT.
V01.00.02 Added dcmTrGroupPortNumber to the index of the dcmTrGroupTable.
V01.00.03 dcmTrGroupType is now read-create ColumnNumbers now follow each other (various tables) Fixed range of transrater group id's, Ts index
V01.00.04 various changes to dpi table, improved documentation
V01.00.05 support two new DPI modes
V01.00.06, DCM 5.0 release support for AutoPass feature
V01.00.07, DCM 5.1 release support for Fec Encoding on GbE OutputTs
V01.00.08, DCM 6.9 release support for Transparent loopthrough and ASI input bandwidth limitations
V01.00.09, DCM 8.0 release support for triggering service backup (per board or per TS) and device backup
V01.00.09, DCM 8.1 release support for service backup and ts backup
V01.00.10, DCM 9.0 release support for IPGW
V01.00.11, DCM 10.10 release support for 4 IPGW boards
V01.00.12, DCM 10.20 release Extended support for service backup (MFP,TC,DVBS2)
V01.00.13, DCM 13.0 release support for GbE port mode
